  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Drafter (Aluminium company)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Drafter / CAD Drafter (Aluminium & Façade Works)</strong></h2><h3><strong>Job Scope / Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Prepare <strong>shop drawings and detailed fabrication drawings</strong> for aluminium windows, doors, curtain wall, façade, louvers, railings, and glazing works.</p></li><li><p>Produce <strong>layout, section, elevation, and detail drawings</strong> based on architectural drawings, specifications, and site conditions.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate drawings with <strong>Project Managers, Engineers, Quantity Surveyors, and Production Teams</strong> to ensure accuracy and constructability.</p></li><li><p>Revise drawings based on <strong>consultant / client comments</strong>, site feedback, and coordination requirements.</p></li><li><p>Prepare <strong>material take-offs and cutting lists</strong> to support procurement and fabrication.</p></li><li><p>Ensure drawings comply with <strong>project specifications, authority requirements, and aluminium system standards</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Assist in preparation of <strong>as-built drawings</strong> upon project completion.</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper <strong>drawing records, revisions, and document control</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Attend coordination meetings or site discussions when required.</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Diploma / Certificate in <strong>Drafting, Civil / Structural / Architectural Technology</strong>, or related field.</p></li><li><p>Experience in <strong>aluminium, façade, glazing, or metal works drafting</strong> is preferred.</p></li><li><p>Proficient in <strong>AutoCAD</strong> (knowledge of Revit or BIM is an advantage).</p></li><li><p>Able to read and interpret <strong>architectural and structural drawings</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Familiar with aluminium systems, profiles, glass types, and basic installation details.</p></li><li><p>Detail-oriented, well-organised, and able to meet deadlines.</p></li><li><p>Good communication skills and able to work independently or in a team.</p></li></ul>",
